The paper proposes a novel task of Manipulation Question Answering (MQA) which involves a robot actively interacting with the environment via manipulation to find the answer to a question. This task involves robotics (cs.RO), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.LG), and natural language processing (cs.CL). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
